title: Nissan.GT.Academy.2013.Episode.3.Speed.Strength.Soul.WEBDL.x264-
description:
Missed the premiere on TV so we have to settle for this.
Direct stream copy from Nissan YouTube channel.
OK quality; Not true HD 720p video.
Prime example why I discourage use of Web Streams as source to convert.
They are further compressed files of previously compressed files.
Note the horrible tiling mess during rapid motion scenes.
